name: aliexpress.solution.feed.list.get
description: API to query the feed list belonged to a seller

requestParams.name: status
requestParams.description: status of the job, currently there are 3 types: FINISH, PROCESSING, QUEUEING

requestParams.name: submitted_time_end
requestParams.description: Search for feeds submitted before a specific time, format: yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm:ss. Timezone:America/Los_Angeles

requestParams.name: submitted_time_start
requestParams.description: Search for feeds submitted after a specific time, format: yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm:ss  .Timezone:America/Los_Angeles

responseParams.name: total_count
responseParams.description: total count of jobs submitted for this seller

responseParams.name: total_page
responseParams.description: total page based on the total_count and page_size
